<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <% include ./header %>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include ./navigation-logged-in %>

    <div class="center-section offset-navbar">
      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="offset-md-2 col-md-6">
          <h1>Question Banks</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2 flex-right">
          <span class="fa fa-plus-square fa-3x" id="add-bank"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="offset-md-2 col-md-8">
          <ul class="question-banks-container" id="main-container">
            <li class="question-bank-card">
              <div class="question-bank-label">
                <span class="fa fa-question-circle-o fa-4x"></span>
                <h1 class="title">Technical Questions</h1>
                <div class="btn btn-3 remove-question-bank">Remove</div>
              </div>
              <ul class="list-group question-bank-questions">
                <li class="list-group-item">Tell me about yourself.<span class="fa fa-close ml-auto"></span></li>
                <li class="list-group-item">What is the importance of closures?<span class="fa fa-close ml-auto"></span></li>
                <li class="list-group-item">What are some of the new features included in ES6?<span class="fa fa-close ml-auto"></span></li>
                <li class="list-group-item">What are the 4 principles of object-oriented programming?<span class="fa fa-close ml-auto"></span></li>
                <input class="list-group-item list-group-item-info mt-2" onKeyPress="onAdd(event, this)"></input>
                <div class="btn btn-2 mt-2 add-question">Add Question</div>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
  <footer>

    <% include ./footer %>
    <script src="javascripts/question-banks.js"></script>
  </footer>
</html>
